&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships with customers that contribute to satisfaction, loyalty, and &lt;strong&gt;long-term retention&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Listen actively&lt;/strong&gt; and adapt your communication style to each customer&#39;s profile and level of technical familiarity&lt;/li&gt;
