&lt;p&gt;As&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Manager&lt;/strong&gt; for the French Market at Amenitiz, your primary objective is to ensure the day-to-day execution, coaching, and operational stability of a small, focused French sales team. You will be a hands-on manager - present in the detail, close to the numbers, and invested in each person&#39;s development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are expected to make the team work: holding the cadence, removing blockers, running the pipeline, and making sure activity translates into results.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We serve independent hoteliers across Europe: family hotels, boutique properties, and small chains that have long been underserved by technology designed for large chains. With over 15,000 customers and a 4.8/5 satisfaction rating, we have a product with proven market fit. You will be leading people who sell something that genuinely makes a difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run daily execution: manage pipeline health, call activity, and meeting volume across the team - BDRs and AEs&lt;/li&gt;
