&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Amenitiz is an all-in-one hotel management platform built for independent hoteliers — PMS, channel manager, booking engine, and website builder in one place. Organic search is one of our most strategic acquisition channels, and this role sits at its centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;As Senior SEO Specialist, you&#39;ll own the end-to-end organic search strategy across five locales (EN, FR, IT, ES, PT), with France as the primary growth market. Your north-star metric is New MRR driven through organic — not just rankings or traffic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re the kind of SEO who thinks beyond rankings, who&#39;s already paying attention to how AI systems surface content, and who wants to build something with real business impact — this role was written for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your missions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Partner with the Content team to ensure all content is SEO, AEO, and AI search optimised across all five locales — briefing, reviewing, and iterating per locale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Own our competitor comparison pages and a 100+ term hospitality glossary programme — systematically improving every page across copywriting quality, SEO, structured data, and AI search visibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Manage technical SEO: hreflang, canonical strategy, JSON-LD structured data (FAQPage, HowTo, BreadcrumbList), Core Web Vitals, and crawl health across our Webflow site.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Own our Answer Engine Optimisation (AEO) strategy — FAQ architecture, featured snippet capture, and People Also Ask coverage across all content types.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Drive our visibility in AI-powered search — optimising content to be cited and recommended by Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, ChatGPT, and Gemini when a hotelier searches for hotel management software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Monitor performance across Google Search Console, GA4, and Semrush — translating data into clear priorities and actions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;3+ years of experience in SEO or digital marketing, with strong knowledge of on-page optimization and content SEO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Solid technical SEO foundations: you can write and validate JSON-LD from scratch, manage hreflang at scale, and diagnose crawl and indexation issues independently.&lt;/li&gt;
